== 發行 ==
電影參加了[[第70屆威尼斯影展|第70屆威尼斯影展]]的競爭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/out-of-competition/ |title=Out of Competition |work=labiennale |accessdate=2013-07-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728070801/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/out-of-competition |archivedate=2013-07-28 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up/ |title=Venice film festival 2013: the full line-up |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=2013-07-25 |location=London |date=2013-07-25 |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725191906/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2014年聖丹斯電影節上首映。於2014年4月18日在英國發布。

於2014年8月12日發行[[藍光光碟|BD]]和[[DVD|DVD]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tribute.ca/movies/dvd/releases/2014/august/august-12/|title=DVD Releases|work=[[Tribute.ca|Tribute.ca]]|accessdate=2014-07-28|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111123814/http://www.tribute.ca/movies/dvd/releases/2014/august/august-12/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《失控》上映後獲得了多為正面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於161條評論持有89％的新鮮度，平均分數7.6／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/locke/ |title=Locke (2014) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2014-08-17 |archive-date=2017-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127040358/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/locke/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據37條評論，得分81（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/locke |title=Locke |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-04-26 |archive-date=2014-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425160822/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/locke |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

